text: Jane Powell (born Suzanne Lorraine Bruce; April 1, 1929 - September 16, 2021) was an American actress. She played the title character in A Date with Judy in 1948. She also played Tess Morgan in Three Daring Daughters (also 1948). Powell was born in Portland, Oregon. She was married to actor Dickie Moore from 1988 until his death in 2015. Powell died of natural causes in Wilton, Connecticut on September 16, 2021 at the age of 92. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Portland, Oregon Category:1929 births Category:2021 deaths Category:American dancers Category:American stage actors Category:Singers from Portland, Oregon
